Libseq C++ Bio sequence library
-------------------------------

Requirements
------------

* cmake (www.cmake.org)
* C++ environment

Build instructions
------------------

Create a temporary build directory (for example within the project root)
The CMAKE_INSTALL_PREFIX variable can point to any directory you want to 
install the libseq headers and library in

$ mkdir build
$ cd build
$ cmake -DCMAKE_INSTALL_PREFIX=~/soft/libseq -DBOOST_PREFIX=~/soft/boost1.52/ ../
$ make

To build the simple test programs
---------------------------------

(Inside the build directory:)

$ make -C test

To install
----------

$ make install

To create the documentation
---------------------------

(In the project root)

$ doxygen

